column4: NSLOCTEXT("[E1CC0F1B4F4E5C58328D178C6BBBA69B]", "4DF528A34193214DF197D29A3A6AEBF0", "If you\'ve heard about us and the city, why don\'t you come with me?")
NSLOCTEXT("[E1CC0F1B4F4E5C58328D178C6BBBA69B]", "65091F684BE56F5850C5F5AB7E595C73", "I\'m also thinking about the island\'s future. I\'ve been searching for something.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E1CC0F1B4F4E5C58328D178C6BBBA69B]", "1EB63CD244077896CF296BA582BCE4DC", "Something that my ancestors left behind, but I don\'t know what it is.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E1CC0F1B4F4E5C58328D178C6BBBA69B]", "B827421D4BEBF9D496B1199CE3B29160", "I see. If I find it, I\'ll let you know.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E1CC0F1B4F4E5C58328D178C6BBBA69B]", "84546A97451E9C6F230B97B27D0EE1A1", "I\'ve been looking a long time. It won\'t be easy to find.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E1CC0F1B4F4E5C58328D178C6BBBA69B]", "4FFC77D64FFF577245F38B9E80FB5240", "But if you find it, I promise, I\'ll go to your city.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E1CC0F1B4F4E5C58328D178C6BBBA69B]", "861E923E406D2E460F9B9D8265480405", "This is what my ancestors had written. Let me see.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E1CC0F1B4F4E5C58328D178C6BBBA69B]", "647043304B83E30EE0E776AEEF32942E", "When danger comes to the island, go to the city.")
NSLOCTEXT("[E1CC0F1B4F4E5C58328D178C6BBBA69B]", "58033EEA4CEE2511F2D3A9B4C48A72A7", "My ancestors say that I should go!")
NSLOCTEXT("[E1CC0F1B4F4E5C58328D178C6BBBA69B]", "09092DC4400F2657887A7681BAE3B717", "I have to look for something. Excuse me, but I have to...")
